  "text": "The proofs of Theorems 1 and 2 are quite technical and require the derivation of several intermediate results, therefore they are omitted in the interest of space. In the following we provide a sketch of the main idea behind their proofs, while for more details the interested reader is referred to [CITATION_1] .",
